        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: new MDT mount option 'noscrub'",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: new MDT mount option 'noscrub'\n\nThe option 'noscrub' disables the mechanism of OI Scrub auto\ntrigger if detects MDT file-level backup/restore when mounts\nup. It allows administrator to configure OI Scrub with more\nflexible parameter(s) as needed after MDT mounts up.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I3cae6f97bf2c4633cb969e10a7e2d6a2fbe1dbf2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
